{"id":142497,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/外交图话：伦敦抗议/","date":"2011-04-02T06:02:04Z","modified":"2011-04-02T06:02:04Z","title":"外交图话：伦敦抗议","content":"<p><p><span><img src=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/files/fp_uploaded_images/110328_TUC_2.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span>3</span><span>月</span><span>26</span><span>号，星期六，</span><span>50</span><span>多万抗议者汇集伦敦中心参加工会组织的示威游行，抗议英国首相卡梅伦削减预算；大多数抗议者很平和，游行人群走过奢华的伦敦西区时，一小部分无政府主义者冲出去攻击了商场，摧毁了警察设置的路障，有近</span><span>200</span><span>人被捕。</span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/files/fp_uploaded_images/110328_TUC_3.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span>防暴警察在哲麦街（</span><span>Jermyn Street</span><span>）燃烧的路障前与示威者发生冲突，伦敦警方称他们动用了</span><span>4500</span><span>名警官。</span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/files/fp_uploaded_images/110328_TUC_4.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span>警察们聚集在议会大厦前，挡住游行队伍。</span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/files/fp_uploaded_images/110328_TUC_5.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span>一名抗议者与警察发生冲突时手里握着烟雾弹。</span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/files/fp_uploaded_images/110328_TUC_6.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span>特拉法加广场悬挂的横幅号召“更换政权”。</span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/files/fp_uploaded_images/110328_TUC_7.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span>游行过程中，警察守护皮卡迪利大街的福特纳姆梅森（</span><span>Fortnum &#038; Masons</span><span>）商厦。</span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/files/fp_uploaded_images/110328_TUC_8.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span>抗议者在牛津广场点燃火把。</span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/files/fp_uploaded_images/110328_TUC_9.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span>一对夫妇装扮成卡梅伦首相和撒切尔夫人的样子，用动作表示反剪他们双手。</span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/files/fp_uploaded_images/110328_TUC_10.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span>警察与示威者在皮卡迪利大街发生冲突。</span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/files/fp_uploaded_images/110328_TUC_11.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span>一名示威者被防爆盾击中脸部。</span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/files/fp_uploaded_images/110328_TUC_12.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span>一名示威者把一组栅栏扔进了皮卡迪利大街一家银行的玻璃门。</span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/files/fp_uploaded_images/110328_TUC_13.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span>一小撮人从平和的抗议队伍中分离出来，冲过皮卡迪利大街，肆意破坏财务，两位上了年纪的妇人观看着。</span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/files/fp_uploaded_images/110328_TUC_14.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span>游行中的暴力行为：一些抗议者袭击警车。</span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/files/fp_uploaded_images/110328_TUC_15.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span>一名无政府主义者用临时停车牌打碎了咖啡店的玻璃。</span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/files/fp_uploaded_images/110328_TUC_16.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span>防暴警察站在哲麦街（</span><span>Jermyn Street</span><span>）燃烧的路障前。</span></p>\n</p>\n<p><b>要翻墙？(发邮件到Gmail):gongminshehui1ATgmail.com</b></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[],"tags":[]}